# Some source files (scripts/score.js in particular) contain unicode box-
# drawing/block characters and emoji in string literals for the terminal
# UI, which confuses `file`'s content-type heuristic into misdetecting
# them as binary — git then shows "Bin X -> Y bytes" instead of a real
# diff. Force text handling explicitly so diffs/blame stay usable.
*.js text
*.md text
*.yml text
*.yaml text
*.json text
